OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784060308
OL,3,CTeaching unions announce formal
OL,4,Cdispute over pay and funding
OL,6,FTwo teaching unions in Wales have
OL,7,Fannounced a formal dispute with the
OL,8,FWelsh Government over teacher pay and
OL,9,Fa lack of support for ALN provision in
OL,10,Fschools.
OL,12,FThe Association of School and College
OL,13,FLeaders (ASCL) and the School Leaders
OL,14,FUnion (NAHT) have written to the Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment issuing a formal trade
OL,16,Fdispute over teacher pay and ALN
OL,17,Ffunding in schools.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
