PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784060308
OL,3,CTeaching unions announce formal
OL,4,Cdispute over pay and funding
OL,6,FThe move comes after the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment chose not to accept the
OL,8,Frecommendation of the Independent
OL,9,FWelsh Pay Review Body (IWPRB) of a
OL,10,F4.2% salary rise for school leaders
OL,11,Fand teachers in September.
OL,13,FInstead, the Welsh Government has
OL,14,Fdecided to consult upon a pay rise of
OL,15,F3.5% for teachers and school leaders
OL,16,Ffor the next academic year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,436,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784060308
OL,3,CTeaching unions announce formal
OL,4,Cdispute over pay and funding
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Welsh Education
OL,7,FMinister Anna Brychan said: "I am
OL,8,Fmindful of the difficult financial
OL,9,Fcircumstances affecting schools and
OL,10,Fcolleges and the implications that
OL,11,Funfunded pay awards would have on
OL,12,Fbudgets and staff numbers.
OL,14,F"The IWPRB recommendation is not
OL,15,Faffordable within existing budgets. In
OL,16,Fcoming to my decision, I have had to
OL,17,Fbalance the available budget and
OL,18,Frecognising and rewarding our
OL,19,Fworkforce."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,436,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784060308
OL,3,CTeaching unions announce formal
OL,4,Cdispute over pay and funding
OL,6,FIn their letter to the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment, the two school leaders'
OL,8,Funions have said their dispute is not
OL,9,Fonly about pay.
OL,11,FThey have raised concerns over funding
OL,12,Fschools to support pupils with
OL,13,FAdditional Learning Needs (ALN).
OL,15,FPaul Whiteman, NAHT's general
OL,16,Fsecretary described the Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment's decision as a "reckless
OL,18,Fapproach".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,436,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784060308
OL,3,CTeaching unions announce formal
OL,4,Cdispute over pay and funding
OL,6,FHe said: "The decision to declare a
OL,7,Ftrade dispute is not one we take
OL,8,Flightly.
OL,10,F"The Welsh Government's failure to
OL,11,Fhonour the independent, carefully-
OL,12,Fconsidered advice of the independent
OL,13,Fpay review body undermines the whole
OL,14,Fprocess.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,436,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784060308
OL,3,CTeaching unions announce formal
OL,4,Cdispute over pay and funding
OL,6,F"It will feel like a slap in the face
OL,7,Ffor leaders and teachers whose pay has
OL,8,Ffallen in value significantly since
OL,9,F2010 at the same time as the pressures
OL,10,Fof the job have increased
OL,11,Fconsiderably, including around ALN
OL,12,Fprovision.
OL,14,F"School leaders are passionate about
OL,15,Fconsistently delivering first-rate
OL,16,Fsupport for pupils with ALN, but too
OL,17,Foften they simply do not have
OL,18,Fresources needed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
