CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784060308
OL,3,CTeaching unions announce formal
OL,4,Cdispute over pay and funding
OL,6,FPepe Di'lasio, ASLC's general
OL,7,Fsecretary, added: "We have taken the
OL,8,Fdecision to register a trade dispute
OL,9,Freluctantly and as a last resort.
OL,11,F"Our members in Wales are not prepared
OL,12,Fto sit by while children with
OL,13,FAdditional Learning Needs miss out on
OL,14,Ffunding which should be invested in
OL,15,Fsupporting them.
OL,26,@oD@SOUsD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,436,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784060308
OL,3,CTeaching unions announce formal
OL,4,Cdispute over pay and funding
OL,6,F"Schools are on their knees trying to
OL,7,Fdeliver provision for all children `
OL,8,Fand particularly those facing the
OL,9,Fgreatest challenges in their lives `
OL,10,Fwithout adequate funding from the
OL,11,FWelsh government.
OL,13,F"It is a situation which is hugely
OL,14,Fdamaging to morale, wellbeing, and
OL,15,Fworkloads, and most importantly, risks
OL,16,Ffailing the children who most need our
OL,17,Fsupport.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,436,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784060308
OL,3,CTeaching unions announce formal
OL,4,Cdispute over pay and funding
OL,6,F"To add insult to injury, the Welsh
OL,7,Fgovernment has not followed the
OL,8,Frecommendation of the independent pay
OL,9,Freview body on the level of teacher
OL,10,Fpay necessary to support recruitment
OL,11,Fand retention.
OL,13,FInterim leader of Welsh Labour, Ken
OL,14,FSkates, told ITV Wales that these
OL,15,Fnegotiations "have to be resolved."
OL,17,FHe added: "There is no other option
OL,18,Fthan to withdraw this supplementary
OL,19,Fbudget" and "to sort out the disputes
OL,20,Fwith trade unions."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
