CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784060308
OL,3,CTeaching unions announce formal
OL,4,Cdispute over pay and funding
OL,6,FIf there's no withdrawal, he said,
OL,7,FLabour MSs will vote against the
OL,8,Fsupplementary budget, meaning that the
OL,9,FWelsh Government is certain to be
OL,10,Fdefeated.
OL,12,FThis issue has been central to
OL,13,Fdiscussions between the new Plaid
OL,14,FCymru Welsh Government and Labour
OL,15,Fahead of a crucial vote on its
OL,16,Fspending plans on Tuesday.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
