OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784060308
OL,3,CTeaching unions announce formal
OL,4,Cdispute over pay and funding
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru was the largest party
OL,7,Fafter May's Senedd election so forms
OL,8,Fthe Welsh Government, but doesn't have
OL,9,Fa majority to pass the supplementary
OL,10,Fbudget alone.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Government are set to lose
OL,13,Fbudget vote as Labour refuse to back
OL,14,Fspending plans.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/11
